# Creative Writing Story Generator

A Python-based tool for generating original fiction stories based on user-defined parameters, inspired by a detailed creative writing prompt. This project creates compelling, structured stories with customizable genres, tones, points of view, lengths, and more, ensuring vivid imagery, emotional resonance, and narrative cohesion.

